TY  - JOUR
T1  - A Direct Numerical Method for a Class of Queueing Problems
AU  - Wijngaard, J.
Y1  - 1978/09/01
PY  - 1978
DA  - 1978/09/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.24.13.1441
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.24.13.1441
